                            <comment id="13263880" author="nspiegelberg" created="Fri, 27 Apr 2012 18:44:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The original idea is to have a timeout when we encounter this error.  Since we have a recoverable ZK, it seems okay to retry after connection loss; but we should have some sort of dampening so that this isn&apos;t a CPU &amp;amp; log hog.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13263891" author="nspiegelberg" created="Fri, 27 Apr 2012 19:04:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch should work for 89fb, 94, and trunk&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
